events.details: A meteor crashes outside of Tokyo Marunouchi Station. The meteor's origins and composition are unknown, but it's energy reading is similar to that of Cores.
events.video_title: The Creation of GiIvaSunner [FILE-01] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: An unknown, wealthy individual purchases the meteor for ¥562315000. He carves a statue out of it, in the image of the ancient Greek figure, Antinous.
events.video_title: The Creation of GiIvaSunner [FILE-01] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The statue comes to life, killing its owner. Reports come in of a synthetic voice saying, "I am GiIvaSunner, I only upload high quality video game rips." GiIvaSunner hijacks a computer, and creates a YouTube channel in his image.
events.video_title: The Creation of GiIvaSunner [FILE-01] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: After ripping video game music for 3 months, the GiIvaSunner YouTube channel receives a copyright strike.
events.video_title: Termination [FILE-02] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: GiIvaSunner apprehends 7 suspects. Most are unidentified except for the crime lord, Dinkleberg.
events.video_title: Termination [FILE-02] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: GiIvaSunner starts his interrogation. Dinkleberg reveals himself to be Angry Joe, who filed the strike against GiIva out of jealousy.
events.video_title: A Big Announcement

events.details: An assault occurs on GiIvaSunner's plane, resulting in him losing an eye and a piece of shrapnel lodging in his head. Joe files another strike, leading to the termination of the GiIvaSunner channel.
events.video_title: A Big Announcement

events.details: GiIvaSunner becomes a lifeless statue, falling into the ocean. Angry Joe disappears, and GiIva's plane crashes with no survivors.
events.video_title: Termination [FILE-02] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: GiIvaSunner is fished out of the ocean and placed back on auction. Chad Warden buys it for $599 USD.
events.video_title: Termination [FILE-02] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Chad Warden takes the statue home. Realizing who it was, he creates the new SiIvaGunner YouTube channel. The statue comes back to life, saying "I am SiIvaGunner, I only upload high-quality video game rips."
events.video_title: Termination [FILE-02] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Chad Warden is not killed by SiIvaGunner. They become allies. Chad buys SiIva a house, computer, and an eyepatch.
events.video_title: Termination [FILE-02] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Chad Warden uploads a video aimed at the fans, criticizing their love for "Meet the Flintstones" rips compared to their hatred for "Snow halation" rips.
events.video_title: MEGALOVANIA (OST Version) - Undertale

events.details: The Voice Inside Your Head, in a state of mania, has visions of a dark future. To prevent catastrophe, he plans on stopping Chad Warden by rebooting the universe.
events.video_title: Recovered Documents [FILE-INT-BLACK] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 is created by Chad Warden, with the purpose of explaining a rip's joke.
events.video_title: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 [FILE-11] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Chad Warden uploads a follow-up video, explaining how "Snow halation" haters should leave it alone, and that it has and always will be a part of the channel's history.
events.video_title: Megalovania (Beta Mix) - EarthBound Halloween Hack

events.details: SiIvaGunner suffers another crash on his ripping software. SiIva heads to The Nigra Store to purchase new software.
events.video_title: Futari Happiness (NOZOMI Mix) - Love Live! School idol festival

events.details: SiIvaGunner is rebooted. The Flintstones, "Snow halation", and the Loud Nigra Scream are replaced with The Simpsons/Family Guy, "GO MY WAY!!", and the Howie Scream.
events.video_title: Intro - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: Chad Warden notices the change in jokes. He is confronted by The Voice Inside Your Head. The Voice tells Chad that he reshaped the universe due to the negative feedback towards "Snow halation".
events.video_title: Now Rebooting - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: After trying to rip Mighty No. 9, a virus is detected. The virus becomes Wood Man, created by The Voice to remember him in case he didn't survive the confrontation with Chad Warden.
events.video_title: Main Theme (Origin) - Mighty No. 9

events.details: The Voice becomes concerned that Chad Warden remembers the old timeline. He decides that he could use Chad, alongside Wood Man, to carry out his plans.
events.video_title: Recovered Documents [FILE-INT-BLACK] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The Voice presents Chad Warden the truth about "Snow halation". The Voice, getting bored of the rebooted universe, presents Chad with multiple deals, including one where the original and rebooted universe combine, but without "Snow halation"
events.video_title: The Deal - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: Chad Warden accepts The Voice's deal. The universes merge, but without "Snow halation". The reboot ends.
events.video_title: A Grand New Era ~Ending~ - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: In an alternate timeline, Chad Warden reveals his true intentions of taking over the SiIvaGunner channel. Chad kills The Voice.
events.video_title: Fly High, No Lies ~Genocide Ending~ - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: Chad Warden kills SiIvaGunner, starting his rampage on the world.
events.video_title: MEGALOVANIA (PS4 Version) - Undertale

events.details: Chad Warden explains to The Voice why "Snow halation" is important to the channel, and that the haters don't matter. The Voice reveals that he had sent JustinRPG to reek havok on the world.
events.video_title: Melody of the Heart ~True Ending~ - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: Chad Warden uses the power of The MF Like Button to bring "Snow halation" back. The Voice is defeated and Chad dies.
events.video_title: Melody of the Heart ~True Ending~ - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: The Green de la Bean is born. SiIvaGunner treats it as his own son.
events.video_title: The Supreme Visitor [FILE-06] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The Bean is killed by Figment radicalists.
events.video_title: The Supreme Visitor [FILE-06] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: SiIvaGunner mourns the death of The Bean with a channel event.
events.video_title: The Supreme Visitor [FILE-06] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: SiIvaGunner, still upset, deletes all of the event's uploads. The channel is overloaded, causing a dimensional rift to form. The Flustered Fernando channel emerges from the rift.
events.video_title: The Supreme Visitor [FILE-06] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: "Wood Man Stage - Mega Man 2" is uploaded to the SiIvaGunner channel without consent. Wood Man uses the rip to escape SiIva's computer.
events.video_title: The Werewolf [FILE-05] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: SiIvaGunner creates his highest quality rip, "Title Theme & Ending - 7 GRAND DAD". He goes to sleep out of exhaustion.
events.video_title: Title Theme & Ending - 7 GRAND DAD

events.details: Wood Man begins work on the Figment Transport Device, allowing Figments to enter the CCC.
events.video_title: The Werewolf [FILE-05] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Under the effects of a full moon, Wood Man turns into The 8-Bit Beast.
events.video_title: The Werewolf [FILE-05] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Wood Man begins uploading Halloween-related rips during The SiIvaGunner Spooktacular Halloween Horror Special.
events.video_title: Ending (Silent Hills Trailer) - P.T.

events.details: The Voice returns, gaining access to SiIva's computer to release Figments into the CCC. Taking President Max P. Haltmann with him, The Voice transforms Rotterdam into Grandiose City.
events.video_title: Prologue - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Pushback of The Voice's takeover is futile. Many of the Figments are captured, leaving Nozomi Tojo alone. She heads off.
events.video_title: Prologue - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice introduces himself to the public. The Cinderella Girls from The iDOLM@STER are executed.
events.video_title: Seasonal Return [Episode 1] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Nozomi is attacked by a Spheric, chasing her down the streets.
events.video_title: Seasonal Return [Episode 1] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice broadcasts a recruitment video, asking for high-quality rips during the Christmas season to boost Christmas Spirit.
events.video_title: YOU can join the fight! - A Recruitment Video from The Voice

events.details: Angry Joe pledges his allegience to The Voice, and gives him SiIva's eye.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The Voice is informed of Nozomi's presence in Grandiose City. Haltmann presents blueprints for The Stringbot.
events.video_title: No Place to Hide [Episode 2] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Rapper's Union, consisting of Snoop Dogg, Chip tha Ripper, Soulja Boy, and Charles Barkley, plan an assault on a Voice-controlled facility.
events.video_title: No Place to Hide [Episode 2] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Nozomi defeats the Spheric. She enters it, becoming its pilot and transforming it into the Smolitzer.
events.video_title: No Place to Hide [Episode 2] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Rapper's Union do their assault. Facing defeat, Nozomi saves them. The Union claims the building as their new base.
events.video_title: No Place to Hide [Episode 2] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The citizens of Grandiose City start rioting. The Stringbots are deployed on them.
events.video_title: Old Times [Episode 3] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice calls Wood Man to his office, ordering him to kill Nozomi. The concept of Figments vs Humans is explained.
events.video_title: Old Times [Episode 3] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Wade L.D. starts his employment at Haltmann Works Company as Administrative Secretary. He survey's SiIva's house.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man confronts Nozomi. He fails to kill her.
events.video_title: Will of a Knight [Episode 4] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Haltmann informs The Voice about plans to ambush the North Pole to gain access to Christmas Spirit.
events.video_title: Haltmann [Episode 5] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Nozomi encounters Meta Knight. He tells her that they must seek out Santa Claus before the ambush. He leaves Nozomi a plate of food.
events.video_title: Will of a Knight [Episode 4] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Robbie Rotten escapes The Voice's tower. Wood Man and Robbie form a partnership of villainy.
events.video_title: Haltmann [Episode 5] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Wade L.D. performs a survey of the barracks. He sends Haltmann information of Angry Joe's assault.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Waluigi begins working at El Bean's restaurant to earn rent money. He creates the Garlic Taco. The taco opens a portal.
events.video_title: Opening Scene - Waluigi's Tacostand

events.details: Haltmann alerts Wade L.D. about The Voice not holding up his end of the bargain.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Haltmann reports strange noises and smells, revealed to be a Garlic Taco on his desk. He takes a bite, opening a portal.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Angry Joe and Nathaniel Welchert lead the ambush, capturing Santa Claus and his workshop. The process of extracting Christmas Spirit begins.
events.video_title: Mechanizing Occupation Project [FILE-13] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Nozomi and Meta Knight arrive at the North Pole. They sneak through the compound, reaching and freeing Santa.
events.video_title: Advent of Hell [Episode 6] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Santa sets off a timer to destroy his workshop, preventing The Voice from obtaining Christmas Spirit. Their plans of escape are thwarted by Angry Joe, who stole Santa's sleigh.
events.video_title: Advent of Hell [Episode 6] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The main trio are stopped by Nathaniel Welchert in a giant spider mech. The Smolitzer defeats Nathaniel, allowing the main trio to escape. Nathaniel dies in the workshop explosion.
events.video_title: Advent of Hell [Episode 6] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Santa explains Christmas Spirit to Nozomi and Meta Knight. The Voice's possible intentions are revealed.
events.video_title: Advent of Hell [Episode 6] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice reflects on the SiIvaGunner channel's 1st anniversary.
events.video_title: [The SilvaGunner Timeline: A Summary of Events]

events.details: Angry Joe reports the destruction of Santa's Workshop to The Voice. Joe gives The Voice a vile of Christmas Spirit.
events.video_title: Loves the Ladies [Episode 7] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice calls Haltmann into his office, presenting his daughter, "Susie", though was actually Haruka Amami in disguise. Haruka performs "The Noble Haltmann".
events.video_title: Loves the Ladies [Episode 7] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Nozomi, Meta Knight, and Santa face off against Angry Joe and Mecha-Dick. The main trio win using Christmas Spirit.
events.video_title: Loves the Ladies [Episode 7] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The main trio and The Rapper's Union come up with a plan to infiltrate The Voice's barracks.
events.video_title: An Acrimonious Assault [Episode 8] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Wood Man and Robbie Rotten capture The Voice's army.
events.video_title: An Acrimonious Assault [Episode 8] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Angry Joe, controlling the Bowflexo mech and using Christmas Spirit, fights the main trio and The Rapper's Union. Nozomi defeats Joe through Haruka's encouragement and Christmas Spirit. Snoop Dogg kills Joe.
events.video_title: An Acrimonious Assault [Episode 8] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice hires Kazoo Master, in exchange of Kazoo rips on the channel.
events.video_title: An Acrimonious Assault [Episode 8] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Pac-Man tries to give crack to Woodsans and Gaijin Goomba. It does not go well.
events.video_title: Main Theme - Pac-Man

events.details: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 is obtained by Haltmann Works Company for testing purposes.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Dr. Andonuts contacts Wade L.D. about obtaining parts for a Joke-Explainer™ 7000 replica. Andonuts asks for the project to be hidden from the company.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wade L.D. and Charles Barkley survey The Rapper's Union's base. Barkley plans his attack.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The Garlic Taco is stolen by 2B, who escapes through a portal.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wade L.D. is tasked with surveying the now destroyed Santa's Workshop.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: 2B contacts Wade L.D. for the first time, telling him that she will contact him soon.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Haltmann asks Wade L.D. to gather parts for a mysterious project against The Voice.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The Voice meets with Charles Barkley to discuss plans against The Rapper's Union.
events.video_title: Timbre of a Kazoo [Episode 9] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Gadgetini Clone 2.0, a robot resembling Inspector Gadget, bursts into The Voice's office. The Voice is kicked out.
events.video_title: Timbre of a Kazoo [Episode 9] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Wood Man and Robbie Rotten ambush the main trio in an attempt to capture the heroes. The duo lose to fire.
events.video_title: Timbre of a Kazoo [Episode 9] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: 2B encounters Snoop Dogg, asking if he has seen Wario or Waluigi. She leaves through a portal.
events.video_title: Timbre of a Kazoo [Episode 9] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Rapper's Union, alongside new member PaRappa, are ambushed by Charles Barkley. Barkley kills Chip and PaRappa, before summoning Kazoo Master. Barkley is sucked into Kazoo Master's portal. Snoop Dogg and Soulja Boy fight Kazoo Master, although Kazoo Master leaves after being bested by Soulja Boy.
events.video_title: Timbre of a Kazoo [Episode 9] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Haltmann disables the Gadgetini Clone 2.0, taking over The Voice's office and the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Wade L.D.'s request for the analyzation of the SiIvaGunner sample is granted. Project AIRTH enters alpha testing, using the sample, parts from the Gadgetini Clone 2.0, and Grand Dad as a power source.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Snoop Dogg rallies the citizens against The Voice and Haltmann. He announces his run for president.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Nozomi, Meta Knight, and Santa head towards The Voice's tower. Loud Nigra helps them break in.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: 2B contacts Wade L.D. again, asking for his help securing internal HWC information.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wade L.D. provides the sample of SiIvaGunner to "third-parties". AIRTH prototypes are developed. A leak occurs, though testing from it is successful.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man shows the viewers the Genocide Timeline, the timeline where Chad Warden kiiled The Voice and SiIvaGunner. He soon brings everyone back to the regular timeline.
events.video_title: Nice, Slick, Blackness - SilvaGunner: Rebooted

events.details: Wade L.D. meets up with 2B, where she explains the time loop. They are confronted by police and drug dealers, but soon escape through a portal.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wade L.D. helps 2B escape, though is presumed dead once the portal closes.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Rob Thomas makes a deal with Haltmann for the SiIvaGunner channel to host "Smooth Day".
events.video_title: Meeting with Haltmann - Kirby Planet Robobot

events.details: Wood Man travels to the A.I. Universe, created by the SiIva A.I.'s testing. Filming of Wood Man's new movie, The SiIvaGunner Spooktacular Halloween Horror Special: Part II begins, starring himself and Takane Shijou. During filming, Wood Man kills Proto. Wood Man's actions cause the rapid evolution of the universe and the A.I.
events.video_title: FEATURE PRESENTATION

events.details: Wood Man presents his movie to Haltmann. Haltmann disregards it, and it is not show in the CCC.
events.video_title: A FEATURE PRESENTATION: ENDING

events.details: Wood Man's deniability of Proto's death causes BonziBuddy to spark many conspiracy theories.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The SiIva A.I. begins recording its own logs. The A.I. reflects on Wood Man's recent actions and a potential tournament.
events.video_title: [SIIVA AI LOG: 2017-11-1]

events.details: The main trio fall into a garbage pit. They find themselves in an underground lab containing Figment cloning experiments run by JustinRPG.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: The Voice, somewhere in the tower, orders JustinRPG to defeat the main trio in exchange for bringing Reshiram to him.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Reshiram eats JustinRPG, though the two return as a fusion, Ju'Reshoggoth. He fights the main trio, causing Santa to lose an arm and the Smolitzer to be destroyed. Ju'Reshoggoth is killed by Santa.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Nozomi, Meta Knight, and Santa enter an elevator, heading to The Voice's tower.
events.video_title: I Love Her [Episode 10] - The SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis

events.details: Project AIRTH concludes alpha testing.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Project AIRTH enters beta testing.
events.video_title: The Life and Times of Wade L.D. - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The SiIva A.I. suffers minor glitches as beta testing begins. These glitches are claimed to be caused by Wood Man.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Wood Man invites Robbie Rotten to dinner, though it ends badly. Wood Man explains that the CCC is stuck in a time loop. They argue about the other being a failure, but make up.
events.video_title: Wood Man & Robbie Rotten - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The SiIva A.I. suffers a major glitch. The glitch manifests Inspector Gadget in the A.I. Universe and takes over the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: You are filled with announcementation.

events.details: The Nostalgia Critic fights Inspector Gadget for control of the channel, ultimately winning.
events.video_title: An AWESOME Announcement

events.details: Due to accusations against him, the Nostalgia Critic releases his control of the channel. The SiIva A.I. reboots itself to fix the glitches.
events.video_title: An AWESOME Announcement

events.details: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 replica is completed. It serves similar functions to the original Joke-Explainer, though runs on Christmas Spirit.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: John Notwoodman hosts the King for a Day Tournament, inviting 16 contenders to fight for the chance to take over the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: SiIvaGunner presents... The KING FOR A DAY TOURNAMENT!

events.details: Voting for the King for a Day Tournament commences, showcasing each contender and their sourcelist.
events.video_title: Vote Responsibly!! (How to Vote) - SiIvaGunner: King for a Day Tournament

events.details: Unregistered HyperCam 2 defeats Off the Hook ft. Glenna Nalira (now Harmony) in the finals, allowing him to take over the SiIvaGunner channel in the near future.
events.video_title: WINNER [Finals] - SiIvaGunner: King for a Day Tournament

events.details: The Crown summons the Fighting Reject Team against the contenders. The Team is swiftly defeated.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: John Notwoodman bids on a haunted mansion, inspired by the Eddie Murphy movie of the same name. He is outbid by Wood Man.
events.video_title: The SiIva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Unregistered HyperCam 2 hosts his takeover of the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: Title Theme - Nickelodeon 3D Movie Maker

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on the success of the King for a Day Tournament. The A.I. also reflects more on Wood Man and Inspector Gadget's Takeover. The A.I. starts plans on a second tournament.
events.video_title: Overworld () - Super Mario Bros. 2

events.details: Reader watches The Christmas Comeback Crisis Episode 13, however is confronted by a creepy-looking Felix the Cat.
events.video_title: Comeback Crisis: The Lost Rip - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Haltmann rushes into The Voice's office, though with half his face missing. He soon dies. The Voice contacts Wood Man, telling him that SiIvaGunner is having a nightmare and creating Halloween Spirit.
events.video_title: Comeback Crisis: The Lost Rip - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Reader shows his brother Jerome the video, with both getting jumpscared.
events.video_title: Comeback Crisis: The Lost Rip - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man, possessed by Halloween Spirit, kills Robbie Rotten. The Voice dies in Wood Man's arms. Wood Man travels to SiIvaGunner's house, where he is confronted by a possessed Grand Dad.
events.video_title: Comeback Crisis: The Lost Rip - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Grand Dad pulls Jerome into CCC-FOOLS and kills him. Wood Man kills Grand Dad, but finds himself surrounded by the other possessed characters.
events.video_title: Comeback Crisis: The Lost Rip - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man pulls Reader into CCC-FOOLS to use as a distraction. The possessed characters are killed by an awoken SiIva. The Halloween Spirit forms into the 8-Bit Beast, but is killed by SiIva. Wood Man returns Reader to "The Real World".
events.video_title: Comeback Crisis: The Lost Rip - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The Grinch, wanting to promote his new movie, takes over the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: Ending - The Grinch

events.details: Getting irritated due to the lack of fanfare for his movie, The Grinch cancels Christmas, posting no more rips.
events.video_title: Ending - The Grinch

events.details: The SiIvaGunner channel is terminated due to receiving copyright strikes from Sony Music Entertainment Japan. The SiIva A.I. starts to malfunction.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: HWC manages to bring the channel back from its termination. The SiIva A.I. becomes responsive again.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 replica takes a bite from a Garlic Taco, transporting her to the A.I. Universe.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: John Notwoodman begins sending out invitations for the King for Another Day Tournament.
events.video_title: Reveal Trailer - SiIvaGunner: King for Another Day Tournament

events.details: Monitoring of Project AIRTH ends. HWC moves to the next phase.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: HWC develops the Quality of Control network to help process the flow of information coming from the SiIva A.I.'s network and SiIvaGunner's thoughts under illucidity.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: Reader, still reeling from Jerome's death, is contacted by Haltmann to help stop the riots in Grandiose City. Reader determines that they need the assistance of Wood Man.
events.video_title: My Last Stand (Funny Jojoke haHA) - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Reader and Haltmann manage to contact Wood Man by building a statue of him in Minecraft.
events.video_title: My Last Stand (Funny Jojoke haHA) - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Return to CCC-FOOLS, Reader, Wood Man, and Haltmann revive The Voice. The Voice becomes concerned about SiIva's awakening, as they no longer have access to his computer to revive the dead Figments.
events.video_title: My Last Stand (Funny Jojoke haHA) - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Reader, Haltmann, Wood Man, and The Voice break into SiIva's house. Haltmann, trying to hack the computer, sets off an alarm, waking SiIva. Reader uses the Dream Machine to revive the Figments, but they are still corrupted. SiIva, holding back the Figments, tells them that they need Easter Spirit.
events.video_title: My Last Stand (Funny Jojoke haHA) - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The guys head to Easter Island. After getting through the Moai, they encounter the Easter Bunny. Wood Man kills him to steal Easter Eggs.
events.video_title: My Last Stand (Funny Jojoke haHA) - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The guys fight the possessed Figments, before bringing them back to normal with Easter Eggs. Wood Man revives Jerome, before returning Reader and Jerome to "The Real World".
events.video_title: My Last Stand (Funny Jojoke haHA) - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man drives to the courthouse, filling in for SiIva who sued by Sony Music Entertainment Japan.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man arrives to court, and faces against Phoenix Wright. Judge Jerome presides over the case, with Wood Man being represented by John Notwoodman.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Both parties give their opening statements. Wood Man is mysteriously missing.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Phoenix Wright calls his witnesses, Mr. YouTube, Bane, and The Grinch. John Notwoodman calls on The Grinch, but lunch is called.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Wood Man goes to the Minion Cafe to enjoy a banana sandwich.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: John Notwoodman manages to catch The Grinch on his bluff, essentially winning the case. John still has to call 3 more witnesses, being Count Cannoli, Nozomi, and Jerome.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The jury returns with a "not guilty" verdict, winning the case for SiIva. Phoenix Wright gets upset and attacks John Notwoodman. Phoenix gets taken away, while Wood Man and Bane leave to get victory lunch.
events.video_title: Unusual Circumstances - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: A masked wooden man breaks into SiIvaGunner's house, busting his pipes and causing leaks for the King for Yet Another Day Tournament to flood his house. (Disclaimer: There is no planned King for Yet Another Day Tournament)
events.video_title: Mass Leakage - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: A group of plumbers consisting of The Grinch, Waluigi, Mr. Beans, Mario, and sphelonious donk, appear to fix the leaks. The Grinch encounters Gay Midi Slappers.
events.video_title: Mass Leakage - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: The Grinch accidentally posts the leaks to the fan discord. Waluigi is sucked through a portal created by a Garlic Taco. Mario is taken away by Monika. SiIva kicks The Grinch out of his house.
events.video_title: Mass Leakage - A SiIvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: John Notwoodman sends out invitations to multiple guests, including Takane, the Joke-Explainer replica, Unregistered HyperCam 2, Princess Heavy, Wolfgirl, and The Dancing Minion, pretending to be Wood Man. He hosts the Halloween party at Wood Man's new mansion.
events.video_title: The SiIvaGunner Spooktacular Halloween Horror Special Part III [Full Movie]

events.details: Proto's brother is murdered in Wood Man's room and is found by the gang. They are confronted by the 8-Bit Beast, who chases them throughout the mansion. The gang find a tied-up Wood Man.
events.video_title: The SiIvaGunner Spooktacular Halloween Horror Special Part III [Full Movie]

events.details: Wood Man is accused of being the 8-Bit Beast and set to burn at the stake. The gang captures the 8-Bit Beast, revealed to be Jeff the Killer, who was hired by John Notwoodman to frame Wood Man after losing the bid for the mansion. John is arrested and sent off to jail.
events.video_title: The SiIvaGunner Spooktacular Halloween Horror Special Part III [Full Movie]

events.details: BonziBuddy relocates to New Engrand to spread his conspiracy theories on Proto's and now Proto's brother's death. He creates the Protonomicon.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on the development of the King for Another Day Tournament and its difficulties. The A.I. also reflects more on Wood Man, including how Wood Man had affected the A.I., John Notwoodman's creation, and Wood Man's actions leading to cult activities.
events.video_title: [SIIVA AI LOG: 2019-11-22]

events.details: John Notwoodman hosts the King for Another Day Tournament. This time, 32 contenders face off yet again to takeover the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: SiIvaGunner presents... The KING FOR ANOTHER DAY TOURNAMENT!

events.details: The Crown takes over Unregistered HyperCam 2, becoming Unrestrained HyperCam 2, in order to make the tournament eternal.
events.video_title: The FINAL BOSS approaches... - SiIvaGunner: King for Another Day

events.details: With the power of The MF Like Button, Mariya Takeuchi and DJ Professor K, alongside the rest of the contenders, defeat The Crown and save Unregistered HyperCam 2.
events.video_title: THIS GAME'S WINNER IS... [FINAL BOSS BATTLE] - SiIvaGunner: King for Another Day

events.details: In the final round of the tournament, DJ Professor K defeats Mariya Takeuchi, allowing him to takeover the SiIvaGunner channel in the near future.
events.video_title: THE TOURNAMENT CHAMPION IS... - SiIvaGunner: King for Another Day

events.details: With the King for Another Day Tournament over, John Notwoodman goes on a break. John and Wood Man reconcile their issues, with Wood Man making a hollow promise to return to the CCC.
events.video_title: Credits - SiIvaGunner: King for Another Day

events.details: Wood Man hosts the SiIvaSummer All-Star Festival, which spans throughout the summer of 2020. Multiple events take place throughout.
events.video_title: The SiIvaSummer All-Star Festival!!

events.details: DJ Professor K hosts his takeover of the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: DJ Professor K's Takeover: Revealed and Comin' To You LIVE! || SiIvaFes

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on the King for Another Day Tournament and the DJ Professor K Takeover. The A.I. starts to experience jealousy and lonliness due to Wood Man's summer festival, where Wood Man received praise while the A.I. stayed in the background.
events.video_title: JET SET RADIO - 24/7 FUNKY FRESH BEATS FROM TOKYO-TO -

events.details: Wood Man releases his new film, Woodyana Stones: Raider Made of Lost Bark.
events.video_title: Volume L Album Announcement || SiIvaFes

events.details: A dark, mysterious carnival comes to town.
events.video_title: ENTRANCE

events.details: The carnival prepares to leave. The arrival of the cursed Fallen Angel is teased for the following year.
events.video_title: EXIT

events.details: The SiIva A.I., trying to replicate Wood Man's success, hosts his own festival. The SiIvaGunner All-Star Winter Festival, filled with many events.
events.video_title: The SiIvaGunner All-Star Winter Festival!

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on the winter festival, detailing the success it has claimed. The A.I. starts to have an identity crisis after learning that it was a copy of the actual SiIvaGunner.
events.video_title: [SIIVA AI LOG: 2020-12-30]

events.details: Metal Ajit Pai has his body forcifully decommissioned by the FCC.
events.video_title: The Silva AI Timeline: A Summary of Events [FILE-INT-AIRTH] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: A powerful demoness known as Lady takes over the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: YANKIN' FOREVER

events.details: Lady is defeated by Knuckles, who uses the Master Emerald to trap her, ending the Yankover.
events.video_title: YANKIN' FOREVER

events.details: Wood Man releases his new film, Legends of the Western Sunset. It coincides with events during The SiIvaGunner All-Star Summer Festival.
events.video_title: The SiIvaGunner All-Star Summer Festival 2021: Legends of the Western Sunset

events.details: The SiIva A.I. hosts the Space Jam Charity SLAM! during the summer festival.
events.video_title: (VOD, Part 1) Space Jam Charity SLAM!

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on the Space Jam Charity SLAM! and Wood Man's new summer festival. The A.I. continues to feel immense isolation about how it can affect the world without actually being seen.
events.video_title: (VOD, Part NaN) Space Jam Charity SLAM!

events.details: In a battle between Knuckles and Dr. Eggman, the Master Emerald is damaged, causing Lady to escape.
events.video_title: LET THE FEAST COMMENCE...

events.details: Takane, suffering nightmares of a potential evil, seeks Wood Man for assistance. The duo encounter Yoshiko "Yohane" Tsushima and a HOBaRT unit left behind by Krusty the Crown and The Joker. The group follow a set of clues.
events.video_title: Curse of the Fallen Angel (COMPLETE AUDIO DRAMA)

events.details: Following the first cluse, the group reach a salsa factory run by Carlito. Surviving the Puzzle Room, the group recover the first cursed, Felix the Cat without his face.
events.video_title: Curse of the Fallen Angel (COMPLETE AUDIO DRAMA)

events.details: Following the second clue, the group head towards the ocean. Locating a spaceship underwater, they encounter a mysterious astronaut. Takane traps the astronaut within an enchanted helmet, obtaining the second cursed.
events.video_title: Curse of the Fallen Angel (COMPLETE AUDIO DRAMA)

events.details: Following the third clue, the group head to space, boarding The Skeld. They encounter a crewmate and Jerma985. The crewmate, being an imposter, attacks Jerma before taking Yohane's form. Takane shoots the crewmate, who was the third cursed. The Skeld starts to plummit towards the ground.
events.video_title: Curse of the Fallen Angel (COMPLETE AUDIO DRAMA)

events.details: The group, including Jerma, survive the crash. They encounter the clowns, who give the group burgers. The poisoned burgers cause them to become unconscious, and Yohane reveals herself to be the true mastermind.
events.video_title: Curse of the Fallen Angel (COMPLETE AUDIO DRAMA)

events.details: The group, being tied up, are freed by Big Chungus and the real Yohane. The fake Yohane reveals herself to be Lady, using the fairgoers to power her ritual. HOBaRT, using the power of the cursed, stops the ritual and banishes Lady to hell.
events.video_title: Curse of the Fallen Angel (COMPLETE AUDIO DRAMA)

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on Lady and her defeats against Knuckles and HOBaRT. The A.I. learns that Lady can hear him, and the two enter in a conversation. The A.I. soon ends the conversation and leaves.
events.video_title: Act : - Curse of the Fallen Angel

events.details: Lady's followers attempt to summon Lady back, however they summon a Twerkey instead. They kill it, and attempt to spread Lady's influence through an album.
events.video_title: A WELL-RECEIVED, GRATITUDE-INDUCING, HIGHLY ANTICIPATED ANNOUNCEMENT

events.details: The SiIva A.I. hosts the Inevitable Holiday Celebration, another super-event though smaller than the festivals. During the event, the Space Jam Charity SLAM! reaches its conclusion.
events.video_title: SiIvaGunner's Inevitable Holiday Celebration!

events.details: The SiIva A.I. reflects on the Inevitable Holiday Celebration. The A.I. continues to feel the lonliness of not being acknowledged for its accomplishments and being ignored by HWC. The A.I. wonders if anyone would notice if it was gone.
events.video_title: [SIIVA AI LOG: 2021-12-25]

events.details: A gust of wind carries Ajit Pai's ashes towards the SiIvaGunner mainframe. Ajit Pai enters the system, taking control of the channel for The Harlem Shakeover.
events.video_title: Hello :)

events.details: Ajit Pai plans to take The Harlem Shakeover worldwide, however is stopped by the antivirus software, sending him to the recycling bin.
events.video_title: PSA from Former Chairman of the FCC Ajit Pai
Intro - Wood Man's Halloween House Party (ft. David S. Pumpkins)

events.details: Susie details the time surrounding Haltmann's death, and how they weren't meant to meet. Susie asks the viewers to assist in creating a bridge between Susie and Wood Man.
events.video_title: Let's discuss business.

events.details: Susie reaches Wood Man, pleading for him to assisst everyone back in the CCC in the final battle. Wood Man believes that he doesn't deserve to go back, but Susie calls him out, explaining that everyone is waiting for his return. Susie leaves Wood Man, letting him remain with his thoughts.
events.video_title: The Meeting - A SilvaGunner Christmas Comeback Crisis Side Story

events.details: Stingy gets his car stolen by Robbie Rotten after destroying his invention. Stingy eventually finds The Joke-Explainer™ 7000's computer, and takes over the SiIvaGunner channel.
events.video_title: [AUDIOLOG: 14:09, RENTAL_STORAGE_FACILITY]

events.details: After taking over the channel for a month, Stingy is visited by The Joke-Explainer™ 7000. The Joke-Explainer tries to get her belongings, but is stopped by Stingy. They make an agreement, where Stingy gives up the laptop in exchange of Joke-Explainer's other belongings.
events.video_title: An announcement from your old leader

events.details: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 returns to running the SiIvaGunner channel, now with the assistance of Dr. Andonuts.
events.video_title: Hi everyone!

events.details: Dr. Andonuts becomes aware that his partnership with Pomni had been discovered by Reader and Jerome in the newest NutshackWoodman34 episode, "My Last Stand".
events.video_title: Nutshackwoodman34 [FILE-18] - Haltmann's Archives

events.details: The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 attempts to celebrate her birthday, but is stopped by Stingy, who takes over the SiIvaGunner channel again due to a clause in the contract.
events.video_title: Announcing my special day!

events.details: Stingy gives back the SiIvaGunner channel to The Joke-Explainer™ 7000 with an apology. Joke-Explainer accepts the apology, and continues operations.
events.video_title: Stingy's Apology
